products.name: Beats Studio 3 Decade Collection
products.description: The Beats Studio 3 Decade Collection Bluetooth headset is a solution that can be used both for working with sound and for comfortable listening to music, watching movies or exciting games. The model uses the Apple W1 chip and large-diameter dynamic emitters. Thanks to their design, as well as support for a wide frequency range, the model can provide high-quality and detailed sound. Another feature of the headphones is the active noise reduction system, thanks to which you can enjoy your favorite music even in the noisiest room.

products.name: Logitech Pro X Lightspeed
products.description: The Logitech G PRO X wired headset is a powerful gaming headset with a stylish black design and a customizable steel headband. Soft headphones with closed acoustics have a memory effect and are complemented by velor breathable pads. The system supports surround sound in 7:1 format using DTS Headphone:X 2.0 7.1 technology, which allows you to detect the enemy by sound.
